radiographic_examinations.procedure_name: CT of the head and chest
radiographic_examinations.findings: A large soft tissue density mass in the right breast measuring approximately 17.1 cm × 13.2 cm × 17.2 cm, with clear borders and regular morphology. No enlarged lymph nodes in the bilateral axillae.
A huge hypoechoic mass with an irregular liquid dark area in the right breast and an enlarged right nipple. No enlargement of cervical, axillary, and inguinal lymph nodes.
A large occupying lesion in the right breast.
